<h2 data-id=3D"5781d18c8931abeca9aea91789b617a7">Command Syntax</h2>
<p data-id=3D"582205add12f2f01afac099faba176c4">The general syntax followed=
 by any Bash command is:</p>
<pre class=3D"cm-viewer-markdown disable-cursor" style=3D"background-color:=
